sub_title: President at Sasak Studio Sejati, Indonesia NTB
summary:
Bachelor and Post-Grad of Theater; specialisation TV and Film media (City Lit. Institute-London).

Theatre work includes:
Une petite Ange du rien du tout - C.A. Puget,
Ring around the Moon - Anouilh,
Midsummer night's Dream - Shakespeare,
The Tempest - Shakespeare,
Rise & Fall of the City of Mahogany - B. Brecht/K. Weil,
She asked for it - Fringe,
Party Games - Fringe,
Punch's Revenge Seagull Theatre
Firebird - Seagull Theatre
Cinderella - Globe Players
Peter and the Dragon - K. Graham.
Millenium - Theatre Stap in de Veste Delft (NL)
All about Adam - NL national tour

Production Experience
Geboren Vrienden - John de Mol Producties

Television:
De Stille Kracht - W. v.d. Kamp
Coronation Street - Granada Television
Goede tijden, slechte tijden.... , EndeMol

Film:
Judges,
Redemption Room


Legal experience in Real Estate, Urban Development at Municipal level.
Diplomatic Corps, Foreign Affairs.
Educational Policy and Cultural Affairs.
Liaison officer in Cultural Associations - SCIIN.
Initiator of Stichting Kebon Sepatu and Founder/Treasurer of Foundation Kebon Sepatu in Indonesia.

Specialties: Inter Cultural Relations and Communication
